high_descs: Turn around and walk to the white table to the left of the black trash bag.
Pick up the knife under the lettuce on the table.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Cut up the leftmost potato in the sink.
Place the knife on top of the egg in the sink.
Pick up a piece of potato from the sink.
Turn around and walk to the stove in the corner.
Place the piece of potato in the pot on the left of the stove.
Pick up the pot on the left of the stove.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Place the pot on the top shelf in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place a pot with a piece of potato in it into the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and head to the white table that has a toaster on it
Grab the knife that is on the table
Turn around and head to the sink
Cut the brown egg in the sink into two slices
Put the knife in the sink
Grab one of the egg slices
Turn left and head to the oven
Put the egg in the large pan on the stove
Grab the large pan off of the stove
Turn around and go to the fridge
Put the pan in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Putting a pan with a sliced egg in it in the fridge

high_descs: turn around, go to white table with toaster on the left
pick up knife under right side of green melon
go to the sink to the right
slice potato in the back left side to the left of the green apple
place knife in sink on top of potato on front, left side
pick up slice of potato
turn around, go to stove on the left
place potato slice in square pan on the left
pick up square pan from stove
go to refrigerator to the right, open refrigerator
place square pan on top shelf of refrigerator, close refrigerator
anns.task_desc: Place square pan with potato slice in refrigerator
